---
import HomeLayout from '../layouts/HomeLayout.astro';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<HomeLayout>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="shell nav">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="文几 WENJI 首页">文几 WENJI <small>MAKES</small></a>
      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="主要导航">
        <a href="#works">作品</a>
        <a href="#latest">最新作品</a>
        <a href="#about">关于</a>
        <a href="#links">链接</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="shell hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-kicker eyebrow">Stardew Valley Mod Creator</p>
          <h1 id="hero-title">做自己想玩、<span>游戏里没有的内容。</span></h1>
          <p class="hero-intro">我是文几。一个“如果游戏里有这个就好了”的念头，最后应该变成真的玩法，而不是停在脑子里。</p>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <a href="#works">看我做了什么 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
            <span class="hero-status">New release<br />Starfall Flute</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="portrait">
          <div class="portrait-frame">
            <img
              src="/images/home/wenji-avatar.jpg"
              width="1254"
              height="1254"
              alt="文几的角色头像：白绿头发、红色眼眸，衣领写着 E=mc²"
              fetchpriority="high"
            />
            <figcaption class="portrait-caption"><b>Creator identity</b>文几 WENJI · 原创 MOD 创作者</figcaption>
          </div>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="manifesto" id="about" aria-labelledby="manifesto-title">
      <div class="shell manifesto-grid">
        <p class="eyebrow">01 / Why I make</p>
        <h2 id="manifesto-title">我想的是玩法，代码只是把它变成真的方式。</h2>
        <div class="manifesto-copy">
          <p>我从“这个游戏缺什么好玩的”开始，而不是从“我还能加什么功能”开始。</p>
          <p><strong>不做简单的数值修改。</strong>我更在意一个 Mod 能不能改变你进入游戏、安排一天和理解世界的方式。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principles" aria-label="创作特点">
          <div class="principle"><b>01 / IDEA</b><span>从一个真正想玩的念头开始</span></div>
          <div class="principle"><b>02 / SYSTEM</b><span>把它做成完整、能运转的规则</span></div>
          <div class="principle"><b>03 / FEELING</b><span>自己玩起来不够有趣，就不发布</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="works" aria-labelledby="works-title">
      <header class="works-head shell">
        <div class="works-title">
          <p class="eyebrow">02 / Selected works</p>
          <h2 id="works-title">我把这些想法，<br />做成了能玩的东西。</h2>
        </div>
      </header>

      <article class="work feature-work ginger-work" id="work-01" aria-labelledby="ginger-title">
        <div class="shell feature-grid">
          <div class="work-number" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
          <a class="feature-visual" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/46543" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Ginger Island Survival">
            <img src="/images/home/ginger-island.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="姜岛求生 Mod：玩家在姜岛海岸醒来" />
            <span class="feature-caption">Released · Nexus Mods</span>
          </a>
          <div class="feature-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">01 / Large-scale opening & narrative</p>
            <h3 id="ginger-title">姜岛求生<span>Ginger Island Survival</span></h3>
            <p>因为太想玩姜岛开局，我自己做了个 Mod。你在岸边醒来，一无所有；探索、求生、搭起营地，再一步步挣回大陆。海盗也会在你攒下足够财富后找上门。</p>
            <div class="feature-list" aria-label="姜岛求生的玩法特点"><span>姜岛开局</span><span>探索求生</span><span>海盗事件</span></div>
            <a class="work-link" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/46543" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">去 Nexus Mods 查看作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="work feature-work fishing-work" id="work-02" aria-labelledby="fishing-title">
        <div class="shell feature-grid">
          <div class="work-number" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
          <a class="feature-visual" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/47586" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Fishing Net">
            <img src="/images/home/fishing-net.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="捕鱼网 Mod：一排渔网布置在海岸水面" />
            <span class="feature-caption">Released · Nexus Mods</span>
          </a>
          <div class="feature-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">02 / Daily rhythm & small system</p>
            <h3 id="fishing-title">捕鱼网<span>Fishing Net</span></h3>
            <p>捕鱼不一定非要一直站在岸边。把渔网放进水里，留它工作一夜，第二天回来收取；耐久度让这套省力的办法依然需要照看。</p>
            <div class="feature-list" aria-label="捕鱼网的玩法流程"><span>放置</span><span>等待</span><span>收取</span></div>
            <a class="work-link" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/47586" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">去 Nexus Mods 查看作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="work feature-work tool-work" id="work-03" aria-labelledby="tool-title">
        <div class="shell feature-grid">
          <div class="work-number" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
          <a class="feature-visual" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/48087" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Universal Tool 天外陨星尺">
            <img src="/images/home/universal-tool.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="天外陨星尺 Universal Tool 作品横幅" />
            <span class="feature-caption">Released · Nexus Mods</span>
          </a>
          <div class="feature-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">03 / Power fantasy & spectacle</p>
            <h3 id="tool-title">天外陨星尺<span>Universal Tool</span></h3>
            <p>能砸、能砍、能收割、能终结木乃伊，还能召唤旋转剑阵。这里不假装追求平衡——它就是为“爽”做的，包括可以改变天气的「天气之子」。</p>
            <div class="feature-list" aria-label="天外陨星尺的玩法特点"><span>故意超模</span><span>全能神器</span><span>天气之子</span></div>
            <a class="work-link" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/48087" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">去 Nexus Mods 查看作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="work feature-work starfall-work" id="latest" aria-labelledby="latest-title">
        <div class="shell feature-grid">
          <div class="work-number" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
          <a class="feature-visual" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/49168" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="在 Nexus Mods 查看 Starfall Flute 星陨魔笛">
            <img src="/images/home/starfall-flute.webp" width="1300" height="372" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="星陨魔笛 Mod：角色在农场吹奏魔笛，身边陈列着不同旋律的曲谱" />
            <span class="feature-caption">New release · Nexus Mods</span>
          </a>
          <div class="feature-copy">
            <p class="eyebrow">04 / Latest release</p>
            <h3 id="latest-title">星陨魔笛<span>Starfall Flute</span></h3>
            <p>它不是按一下按钮就结算的工具。先找到魔笛，再从商店、限时信件、NPC 故事和秘密仪式中学会六首旋律；角色真正吹奏，乐句、动画和视觉演出走到高潮后，浇水、催熟、控怪、归家与惊雷才会发生。</p>
            <div class="feature-list" aria-label="星陨魔笛的玩法特点"><span>六首旋律</span><span>剧情式获取</span><span>音乐施法</span></div>
            <a class="work-link" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/49168" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">去 Nexus Mods 查看作品 <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="next" aria-labelledby="next-title">
      <div class="shell next-grid">
        <p class="eyebrow">03 / What comes next</p>
        <div class="next-copy">
          <h2 id="next-title">Mod 不是终点，<br />是我开始做游戏的地方。</h2>
          <p>接下来，我会继续把姜岛求生扩成更大的作品，也会去别的游戏里试新的想法。长远一点，我想做出真正属于自己的游戏。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="future-list" aria-label="未来方向">
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 01</b><span>姜岛求生大型拓展</span></div>
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 02</b><span>更多游戏里的 Mod 实验</span></div>
          <div class="future-item"><b>NEXT / 03</b><span>自己的独立游戏</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer" id="links">
    <div class="shell footer-main">
      <h2 class="footer-title">我是文几。<br /><span>想玩的东西，我会自己做出来。</span></h2>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a class="footer-link" href="https://xhslink.com/m/7mGN7KQWYMl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <span class="footer-link-meta" aria-hidden="true"><span>01</span><span class="arrow">↗</span></span>
          <strong>小红书</strong>
          <span class="footer-link-note">日常与制作过程</span>
        </a>
        <a class="footer-link" href="https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/users/179201778" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <span class="footer-link-meta" aria-hidden="true"><span>02</span><span class="arrow">↗</span></span>
          <strong>Nexus Mods</strong>
          <span class="footer-link-note">下载与更新</span>
        </a>
        <a class="footer-link" href="https://ko-fi.com/wenjimods" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <span class="footer-link-meta" aria-hidden="true"><span>03</span><span class="arrow">↗</span></span>
          <strong>Ko-fi</strong>
          <span class="footer-link-note">支持我的创作</span>
        </a>
        <a class="footer-link" href="mailto:wenjimakes@gmail.com">
          <span class="footer-link-meta" aria-hidden="true"><span>04</span><span class="arrow">↗</span></span>
          <strong>写邮件</strong>
          <span class="footer-link-note">wenjimakes@gmail.com</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shell footer-bottom">
      <span>© {year} 文几 WENJI</span>
      <span>Made for ideas that should exist.</span>
    </div>
  </footer>
</HomeLayout>